    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. While the engine and transmission perform reliably and have been regularly serviced, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading in the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the cabin is clean but shows significant wear on the driver's seat upholstery and some of the dashboard buttons. It passed its last inspection, but the buyer should expect to address some minor suspension noise in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics.",
