    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and well-loved ride? This car is in great shape and ready for its next adventure! It has been well-maintained, offering a smooth driving experience and a clean, comfortable interior. While it shows a few signs of careful use, it remains a solid, dependable vehicle that looks fantastic on the road. Perfect for anyone seeking quality and performance without the showroom price tag!",
