    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still turns heads? I'm selling my trusty car and it's in really solid shape! It\u2019s been super dependable for me and is ready to hit the road with a new owner. It runs beautifully and has been well-cared for. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
