    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a meticulously maintained E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a recalibrated double-VANOS system for optimal cam timing. This example utilizes the Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission, delivering torque to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive cooling system overhaul. Suspension geometry remains true with refreshed control arm bushings and dampers, ensuring the communicative steering and lateral grip synonymous with the M-division's engineering. A mechanically sound driver's car with excellent throttle response and structural integrity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Maintenance records available. Clean title. Runs well.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 Luxury AWD SUV that strikes the perfect balance between rugged capability and refined elegance. This vehicle has been garage-kept and treated with the utmost care throughout its life. The exterior finish retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front valence\u2014typical for a vehicle that has enjoyed the open road. Inside, the premium leather upholstery remains supple and rich, with only very light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster and no tears or stains. Every electronic feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the premium surround-sound system and navigation, functions exactly as it should. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health; I have a complete folder of every oil change and scheduled maintenance performed by certified technicians. The tires have roughly 70% tread remaining, and the brakes are firm and responsive. This is a reliable, sophisticated vehicle that has been genuinely loved rather than just driven.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
